</script></div></div><div id="meta">Page modified: Wednesday, July 13, 2011 00:38:51<br /></div><p><b>The taking of hostages</b> is a criminal offence against the personal liberty and particularly against the physical integrity of the particular. The taking of hostages is regulated in the German penal code in "? 239b StGB.</p><div id="bodyAd1"><script type="text/javascript"><!--
